				<td colspan="2"><span>Yes, indeed, I do.  I don't enjoy soloing or swarm kiting for AAs though.
<br />

<br />
I thoroughly enjoy being in a group and knowing that my character is making the group much better and making the machine run quieter (less stress, less anguish, less inane finger pointing).
<br />

<br />
By the same token, I've found that I don't really enjoy playing in group that is severely overgeared for an encounter, one where a bard is really superfluous.  I'd rather be in a tight situation needing pulling and CC skills than watch a beastlord pull five mobs and tank four of them with no trouble.  
<br />

<br />
